{"tid":1894992,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 慎防肺炎疫情　最終決定取消首爾演唱會！","createTime":"2020-02-24T09:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T10:09:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e2a924421a82a10f90237556cf253503eae9cdb","tid":1894992,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"不久前 JYP 才剛宣布 TWICE 會如期舉行首爾場演唱會，沒想到疫情在一週內急轉直下，一起來看看 JYP 今天的新公告！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 今天（24 日）中午發出公告，開門見山便表示因為 COVID-19 持續擴散，因此原定於 3 月 7、8 兩日舉行的《TWICELIGHTS in Seoul &ldquo;Finale&rdquo;》將會取消。<br />\n<br />\n由於《TWICELIGHTS in Seoul &ldquo;Finale&rdquo;》是 TWICE 世界巡迴演唱會的壓軸場，在宣佈消息後早已令各國 ONCE 十分期待，TWICE 也一直努力準備帶來全新表演，因此 JYP Entertainment 也特地向粉絲致歉。<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 強調：「我們為了優先考量藝人和粉絲的健康和安全，並積極配合政府的防疫方針，決定盡可能不要舉行讓許多人在室內聚集的活動，因此最終決定取消本次公演。」之後 JYP 將另行公吿退票及退費事宜，周邊商品則會改成線上販賣，ONCE 別忘了多關注消息囉！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/124544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F124544&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=e5acdc55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/124544</a>"},{"pid":"42e5d42c030cecfae42ab053bc01b6062ba524e5","tid":1894992,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"掛住twice了!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/cf6d036bbf9b747370936ac6fec25c87/557a530f425934bd-3b/s250x400/b795adeda9f608ef50f6e0ace75cb503b99237a6.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fcf6d036bbf9b747370936ac6fec25c87%2F557a530f425934bd-3b%2Fs250x400%2Fb795adeda9f608ef50f6e0ace75cb503b99237a6.gifv&h=ad5d4738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/63f8785b32f8ef2ac84bd06bb22312ec/557a530f425934bd-80/s250x400/596cc88f94c5a6040eeb5f86913ff390470c7f62.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.